{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":872,"text":"I'd like to start, if I may,"},{"time":2416,"text":"with the story of the Paisley snail."},{"time":5140,"text":"On the evening of the 26th of August, 1928,"},{"time":8355,"text":"May Donoghue took a train from Glasgow"},{"time":10729,"text":"to the town of Paisley, seven miles east of the city,"},{"time":13260,"text":"and there at the Wellmeadow Caf√©,"},{"time":15573,"text":"she had a Scots ice cream float,"},{"time":18699,"text":"a mix of ice cream and ginger beer"},{"time":20546,"text":"bought for her by a friend."},{"time":22501,"text":"The ginger beer came in a brown, opaque bottle"},{"time":24902,"text":"labeled \"D. Stevenson, Glen Lane, Paisley.\""},{"time":28765,"text":"She drank some of the ice cream float,"},{"time":30841,"text":"but as the remaining ginger beer was poured"},{"time":32675,"text":"into her tumbler,"},{"time":34071,"text":"a decomposed snail"},{"time":36524,"text":"floated to the surface of her glass."},{"time":39106,"text":"Three days later, she was admitted"},{"time":40650,"text":"to the Glasgow Royal Infirmary"},{"time":42156,"text":"and diagnosed with severe gastroenteritis"},{"time":44214,"text":"and shock."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46167,"text":"The case of Donoghue vs. Stevenson that followed"},{"time":49435,"text":"set a very important legal precedent:"},{"time":52080,"text":"Stevenson, the manufacturer of the ginger beer,"},{"time":53811,"text":"was held to have a clear duty of care"},{"time":56588,"text":"towards May Donoghue,"},{"time":58036,"text":"even though there was no contract between them,"},{"time":60138,"text":"and, indeed, she hadn't even bought the drink."},{"time":62955,"text":"One of the judges, Lord Atkin, described it like this:"},{"time":65974,"text":"You must take care to avoid acts or omissions"},{"time":68884,"text":"which you can reasonably foresee"},{"time":70952,"text":"would be likely to injure your neighbor."},{"time":74180,"text":"Indeed, one wonders that without a duty of care,"},{"time":76523,"text":"how many people would have had to suffer"},{"time":78269,"text":"from gastroenteritis before Stevenson\neventually went out of business."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81993,"text":"Now please hang on to that Paisley snail story,"},{"time":84374,"text":"because it's an important principle."},{"time":87607,"text":"Last year, the Hansard Society,\na nonpartisan charity"},{"time":90101,"text":"which seeks to strengthen parliamentary democracy"},{"time":92007,"text":"and encourage greater public involvement in politics"},{"time":95244,"text":"published, alongside their annual audit"},{"time":97831,"text":"of political engagement, an additional section"},{"time":100704,"text":"devoted entirely to politics and the media."},{"time":103827,"text":"Here are a couple of rather depressing observations"},{"time":106202,"text":"from that survey."},{"time":108210,"text":"Tabloid newspapers do not appear"},{"time":110375,"text":"to advance the political citizenship of their readers,"},{"time":113208,"text":"relative even to those"},{"time":114781,"text":"who read no newspapers whatsoever."},{"time":118007,"text":"Tabloid-only readers are twice as likely to agree"},{"time":120999,"text":"with a negative view of politics"},{"time":122850,"text":"than readers of no newspapers."},{"time":125425,"text":"They're not just less politically engaged."},{"time":127418,"text":"They are consuming media that reinforces"},{"time":129866,"text":"their negative evaluation of politics,"},{"time":131828,"text":"thereby contributing to a fatalistic and cynical"},{"time":134931,"text":"attitude to democracy and their own role within it."},{"time":138266,"text":"Little wonder that the report concluded that"},{"time":140426,"text":"in this respect, the press, particularly the tabloids,"},{"time":143616,"text":"appear not to be living up to the importance"},{"time":145955,"text":"of their role in our democracy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":148591,"text":"Now I doubt if anyone in this room would seriously"},{"time":150650,"text":"challenge that view."},{"time":152097,"text":"But if Hansard are right, and they usually are,"},{"time":154713,"text":"then we've got a very serious problem on our hands,"},{"time":156689,"text":"and it's one that I'd like to spend the next 10 minutes"},{"time":159324,"text":"focusing upon."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161353,"text":"Since the Paisley snail,"},{"time":163036,"text":"and especially over the past decade or so,"},{"time":165500,"text":"a great deal of thinking has been developed"},{"time":167419,"text":"around the notion of a duty of care"},{"time":169278,"text":"as it relates to a number of aspects of civil society."},{"time":171817,"text":"Generally a duty of care arises when one individual"},{"time":174561,"text":"or a group of individuals undertakes an activity"},{"time":177295,"text":"which has the potential to cause harm to another,"},{"time":179825,"text":"either physically, mentally or economically."},{"time":182539,"text":"This is principally focused on obvious areas,"},{"time":185010,"text":"such as our empathetic response\nto children and young people,"},{"time":188052,"text":"to our service personnel, and\nto the elderly and infirm."},{"time":190778,"text":"It is seldom, if ever, extended\nto equally important arguments"},{"time":194971,"text":"around the fragility of our\npresent system of government,"},{"time":199221,"text":"to the notion that honesty, accuracy and impartiality"},{"time":202730,"text":"are fundamental to the process of building"},{"time":204874,"text":"and embedding an informed,"},{"time":206603,"text":"participatory democracy."},{"time":209360,"text":"And the more you think about it,"},{"time":210781,"text":"the stranger that is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":212612,"text":"A couple of years ago, I had the pleasure"},{"time":214074,"text":"of opening a brand new school"},{"time":215828,"text":"in the northeast of England."},{"time":217399,"text":"It had been renamed by its pupils as Academy 360."},{"time":220938,"text":"As I walked through their impressive,"},{"time":222790,"text":"glass-covered atrium,"},{"time":224165,"text":"in front of me, emblazoned on the wall"},{"time":225983,"text":"in letters of fire"},{"time":227531,"text":"was Marcus Aurelius's famous injunction:"},{"time":230632,"text":"If it's not true, don't say it;"},{"time":233487,"text":"if it's not right, don't do it."},{"time":236570,"text":"The head teacher saw me staring at it,"},{"time":238558,"text":"and he said, \"Oh, that's our school motto.\""},{"time":241350,"text":"On the train back to London,"},{"time":243077,"text":"I couldn't get it out of my mind."},{"time":244931,"text":"I kept thinking, can it really have taken us"},{"time":247490,"text":"over 2,000 years to come to terms"},{"time":249701,"text":"with that simple notion"},{"time":251566,"text":"as being our minimum expectation of each other?"},{"time":254518,"text":"Isn't it time that we develop this concept"},{"time":257126,"text":"of a duty of care"},{"time":258795,"text":"and extended it to include a care"},{"time":261221,"text":"for our shared but increasingly\nendangered democratic values?"},{"time":264485,"text":"After all, the absence of a duty of care"},{"time":266342,"text":"within many professions"},{"time":267932,"text":"can all too easily amount to\naccusations of negligence,"},{"time":270435,"text":"and that being the case, can we be\nreally comfortable with the thought"},{"time":273542,"text":"that we're in effect being negligent"},{"time":275843,"text":"in respect of the health of our own societies"},{"time":278634,"text":"and the values that necessarily underpin them?"},{"time":281369,"text":"Could anyone honestly suggest, on the evidence,"},{"time":284364,"text":"that the same media which\nHansard so roundly condemned"},{"time":287620,"text":"have taken sufficient care to avoid behaving"},{"time":290907,"text":"in ways which they could reasonably have foreseen"},{"time":294349,"text":"would be likely to undermine or even damage"},{"time":296450,"text":"our inherently fragile democratic settlement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299284,"text":"Now there will be those who will argue"},{"time":301305,"text":"that this could all too easily drift into a form"},{"time":303078,"text":"of censorship, albeit self-censorship,"},{"time":305085,"text":"but I don't buy that argument."},{"time":307041,"text":"It has to be possible"},{"time":309100,"text":"to balance freedom of expression"},{"time":311200,"text":"with wider moral and social responsibilities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314407,"text":"Let me explain why by taking the example"},{"time":316258,"text":"from my own career as a filmmaker."},{"time":319161,"text":"Throughout that career, I never accepted"},{"time":320968,"text":"that a filmmaker should set about putting"},{"time":322595,"text":"their own work outside or above what he or she"},{"time":325645,"text":"believed to be a decent set of values"},{"time":327595,"text":"for their own life, their own family,"},{"time":330944,"text":"and the future of the society in which we all live."},{"time":334535,"text":"I'd go further."},{"time":335859,"text":"A responsible filmmaker should\nnever devalue their work"},{"time":339153,"text":"to a point at which it becomes less than true"},{"time":341197,"text":"to the world they themselves wish to inhabit."},{"time":344637,"text":"As I see it, filmmakers, journalists, even bloggers"},{"time":348023,"text":"are all required to face up to the social expectations"},{"time":350547,"text":"that come with combining the\nintrinsic power of their medium"},{"time":354302,"text":"with their well-honed professional skills."},{"time":357676,"text":"Obviously this is not a mandated duty,"},{"time":360563,"text":"but for the gifted filmmaker\nand the responsible journalist"},{"time":363045,"text":"or even blogger, it strikes me\nas being utterly inescapable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366865,"text":"We should always remember that our notion"},{"time":369464,"text":"of individual freedom and\nits partner, creative freedom,"},{"time":372355,"text":"is comparatively new"},{"time":374150,"text":"in the history of Western ideas,"},{"time":376412,"text":"and for that reason, it's often undervalued"},{"time":378330,"text":"and can be very quickly undermined."},{"time":380693,"text":"It's a prize easily lost,"},{"time":382920,"text":"and once lost, once surrendered,"},{"time":384683,"text":"it can prove very, very hard to reclaim."},{"time":388000,"text":"And its first line of defense"},{"time":389525,"text":"has to be our own standards,"},{"time":391876,"text":"not those enforced on us by a censor or legislation,"},{"time":395615,"text":"our own standards and our own integrity."},{"time":397438,"text":"Our integrity as we deal with those"},{"time":399432,"text":"with whom we work"},{"time":400980,"text":"and our own standards as we operate within society."},{"time":404605,"text":"And these standards of ours"},{"time":406075,"text":"need to be all of a piece with\na sustainable social agenda."},{"time":409340,"text":"They're part of a collective responsibility,"},{"time":411453,"text":"the responsibility of the artist or the journalist"},{"time":413583,"text":"to deal with the world as it really is,"},{"time":415957,"text":"and this, in turn, must go hand in hand"},{"time":418406,"text":"with the responsibility of those governing society"},{"time":420824,"text":"to also face up to that world,"},{"time":422901,"text":"and not to be tempted to misappropriate"},{"time":425276,"text":"the causes of its ills."},{"time":427853,"text":"Yet, as has become strikingly clear"},{"time":430499,"text":"over the last couple of years,"},{"time":432567,"text":"such responsibility has to a very great extent"},{"time":434601,"text":"been abrogated by large sections of the media."},{"time":437644,"text":"And as a consequence, across the Western world,"},{"time":439584,"text":"the over-simplistic policies of the parties of protest"},{"time":442883,"text":"and their appeal to a largely disillusioned,"},{"time":445268,"text":"older demographic,"},{"time":446657,"text":"along with the apathy and obsession with the trivial"},{"time":448865,"text":"that typifies at least some of the young,"},{"time":450763,"text":"taken together, these and other similarly"},{"time":452821,"text":"contemporary aberrations"},{"time":454902,"text":"are threatening to squeeze the life"},{"time":456949,"text":"out of active, informed debate and engagement,"},{"time":460523,"text":"and I stress active."}]},{"cues":[{"time":463050,"text":"The most ardent of libertarians might argue"},{"time":465327,"text":"that Donoghue v. Stevenson should\nhave been thrown out of court"},{"time":468321,"text":"and that Stevenson would eventually\nhave gone out of business"},{"time":470439,"text":"if he'd continued to sell ginger beer with snails in it."},{"time":473856,"text":"But most of us, I think, accept some small role"},{"time":477270,"text":"for the state to enforce a duty of care,"},{"time":480348,"text":"and the key word here is reasonable."},{"time":483020,"text":"Judges must ask, did they take reasonable care"},{"time":486600,"text":"and could they have reasonably foreseen"},{"time":488015,"text":"the consequences of their actions?"},{"time":490213,"text":"Far from signifying overbearing state power,"},{"time":493195,"text":"it's that small common sense test of reasonableness"},{"time":496720,"text":"that I'd like us to apply to those in the media"},{"time":499379,"text":"who, after all, set the tone and the content"},{"time":501650,"text":"for much of our democratic discourse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":504967,"text":"Democracy, in order to work, requires that"},{"time":507687,"text":"reasonable men and women take\nthe time to understand and debate"},{"time":510635,"text":"difficult, sometimes complex issues,"},{"time":512967,"text":"and they do so in an atmosphere which strives"},{"time":515260,"text":"for the type of understanding that leads to,"},{"time":517659,"text":"if not agreement, then at least a productive"},{"time":519726,"text":"and workable compromise."},{"time":522093,"text":"Politics is about choices,"},{"time":524450,"text":"and within those choices, politics is about priorities."},{"time":528441,"text":"It's about reconciling conflicting preferences"},{"time":530979,"text":"wherever and whenever possibly based on fact."},{"time":536195,"text":"But if the facts themselves are distorted,"},{"time":538666,"text":"the resolutions are likely only\nto create further conflict,"},{"time":542389,"text":"with all the stresses and strains on society"},{"time":544276,"text":"that inevitably follow."},{"time":546492,"text":"The media have to decide:"},{"time":548439,"text":"Do they see their role as being to inflame"},{"time":551613,"text":"or to inform?"},{"time":553943,"text":"Because in the end, it comes down to a combination"},{"time":556805,"text":"of trust and leadership."}]},{"cues":[{"time":559296,"text":"Fifty years ago this week,\nPresident John F. Kennedy"},{"time":561873,"text":"made two epoch-making speeches,"},{"time":563479,"text":"the first on disarmament\nand the second on civil rights."},{"time":566976,"text":"The first led almost immediately"},{"time":569078,"text":"to the Nuclear Test Ban Treaty,"},{"time":570659,"text":"and the second led to the 1964 Civil Rights Act,"},{"time":573724,"text":"both of which represented giant leaps forward."},{"time":577310,"text":"Democracy, well-led and well-informed,"},{"time":579715,"text":"can achieve very great things,"},{"time":582208,"text":"but there's a precondition."},{"time":583881,"text":"We have to trust that those making those decisions"},{"time":587192,"text":"are acting in the best interest not of themselves"},{"time":589659,"text":"but of the whole of the people."},{"time":591423,"text":"We need factually-based options,"},{"time":594502,"text":"clearly laid out,"},{"time":595741,"text":"not those of a few powerful"},{"time":597139,"text":"and potentially manipulative corporations"},{"time":599236,"text":"pursuing their own frequently narrow agendas,"},{"time":601603,"text":"but accurate, unprejudiced information"},{"time":604032,"text":"with which to make our own judgments."},{"time":606408,"text":"If we want to provide decent, fulfilling lives"},{"time":608302,"text":"for our children and our children's children,"},{"time":610613,"text":"we need to exercise to the\nvery greatest degree possible"},{"time":613730,"text":"that duty of care for a vibrant,"},{"time":615442,"text":"and hopefully a lasting, democracy."},{"time":618339,"text":"Thank you very much for listening to me."},{"time":620422,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}